'''伯明罕市旗''' （flag of Birmingham）是英國城市[[伯明翰|伯明翰]]的市旗，於2015年開始使用。旗幟圖案系由公開遴選產生<ref>{{Cite news|url = http://www.birminghammail.co.uk/news/midlands-news/bully-birmingham-peoples-competition-9712395|title = Bully For Birmingham: People's Flag Competition Announced|last = Elkes|first = Neil|date = 23 July 2015|work = |access-date = |via = }}</ref>，由均為11歲湯瑪斯·基奧（Thomas Keogh）和大衛·史密斯（David Smith）設計<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/flags/birmingham-warwickshire/ |title=The UK Flag Registry: Birmingham, Warwickshire |accessdate=2016-02-24 |archive-date=2019-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190222221939/http://www.flaginstitute.org/wp/flags/birmingham-warwickshire/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。舊有的紋章圖案市旗僅剩伯明罕議會單獨使用。

